import React,{useEffect,useState} from 'react' import { Card,CardContent,Typography } from '@material-ui/core' const Post = () => { const[posts, setposts]=useState([]) useEffect(() => { const url="https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts" fetch(url) .then(response=>response.json()) .then(response=>setposts(response)) }, []) return ( <> Posts
{posts.map(post=><>

{`${post.id}. ${post.title}`}

{post.body} )}
) } export default Post
